headline: AXA XL Appoints Sylvain Bouteillé as Chief Underwriting Officer, Specialty, Americas
summary: AXA XL is pleased to announce the appointment of Sylvain Bouteillé as Chief Underwriting Officer for Specialty Americas. In this key leadership role, Mr. Bouteillé will oversee the development and execution of AXA XL's regional strategy for its Specialty insurance division which includes Aviation, Ocean Marine, Political Risk, Trade Credit & Commercial Bonds, War, Terrorism & Political Violence, Fine Art & Specie, and Structured Risk Solutions.
